      <title>美光斥资 70 亿美元在新加坡建设内存芯片工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/micron-to-spend-7-billion-building-singapore-memory-chip-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人工智能推动了对先进内存芯片的需求，美光科技公司将在未来几年投资 70 亿美元扩大其在新加坡的制造业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/micron-to-spend-7-billion-building-singapore-memory-chip-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
